data.description: OPEN HOUSE ON JANUARY 21 FROM 2-4. Welcome home! This adorable ranch style home on 1.3 acres in Silverhill is just what you've been looking for. Featuring 3 bedrooms, primary en suite and split floor plan, large open living room, eat in kitchen, and laundry room. What more could you ask for? Luxury vinyl plank flooring in all common rooms and warm carpet in the large bedrooms. Primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet, stand up shower and linen closet. Outside find a fully fenced yard with a gate at the entrance to the driveway and a large storage shed. Enjoy some sweet tea or coffee on the front porch with some rocking chairs! Get it before it's gone! Call your favorite agent today for a private tour.
